ummary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CanvasGradient\"><code>CanvasGradient</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CanvasPattern\"><code>CanvasPattern</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D\"><code>CanvasRenderingContext2D</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/ImageBitmap\"><code>ImageBitmap</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/ImageBitmapRenderingContext\"><code>ImageBitmapRenderingContext</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ImageData\"><code>ImageData</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/OffscreenCanvas\"><code>OffscreenCanvas</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Path2D\"><code>Path2D</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TextMetrics\"><code>TextMetrics</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/createImageBitmap\"><code>createImageBitmap</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\">\n<div id=\"sect2\">\n<div id=\"sect3\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<p>TLa propiedad  <strong><code><span>HTMLCanvasElement.width</span></code></strong> es un entero positivo que refleja el atributo <a href=\"/es/docs/Web/HTML/Element/canvas#attr-width\"><code>width</code></a> del elemento <a href=\"/es/docs/Web/HTML/Element/canvas\"><code>&lt;canvas&gt;</code></a> interpretado en pixeles CSS. Cuando el atributo no esta especificado o se define con un valor invalido (ej. Número negativo), es usado el valor por defecto de 150.</p>\n\n<p>Esta es una de de las dos propiedades que controlan el tamaño del canvas, siendo la otra <a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/HTMLCanvasElement/height\"><code>HTMLCanvasElement.height</code></a>, that controls the size of the canvas.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"Syntax","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\"><var>var <em>pxl</em> = <em>canvas</em></var>.width;\n<em>canvas</em>.width = <em>pxl</em>;\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"ejemplos","title":"Ejemplos","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Dado el siguiente elemento <a href=\"/es/docs/Web/HTML/Element/canvas\"><code>&lt;canvas&gt;</code></a> :</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>canvas</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">id</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>canvas<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">width</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>300<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">height</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>300<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>canvas</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>\n\n<p>Puedes obtener el ancho del canvas con el siguiente codigo:</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> canvas <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getElementById</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"canvas\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nconsole<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>canvas<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>width<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// 300</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"especificaciones","title":"Especificaciones","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Especificación</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Comentarios</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/scripting.html#attr-canvas-width\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML Living Standard<br><small lang=\"es\">La definición de 'HTMLCanvasElement.width' en esta especificación.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-living\">Living Standard</span></td>\n   <td>No hay cambios desde la ultima foto <a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/html52/\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" title=\"La especificación 'HTML5'\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML5</a></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/html51/scripting-1.html#attr-canvas-width\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML 5.1<br><small lang=\"es\">La definición de 'HTMLCanvasElement.width' en esta especificación.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-rec\">Recommendation</span></td>\n   <td> </td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/html52/scripting-1.html#attr-canvas-width\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML5<br><small lang=\"es\">La definición de 'HTMLCanvasElement.width' en esta especificación.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-rec\">Recommendation</span></td>\n   <td>Foto que contiene la definición inicial <a href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" title=\"La especificación 'HTML Living Standard'\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML Living Standard</a>.</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Compatibilidad de Navegadores","id":"compatibilidad_de_navegadores","isH3":false,"query":"api.HTMLCanvasElement.width","dataURL":"/es/docs/Web/API/HTMLCanvasElement/width/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"see_also","title":"Ver también","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li>La interfaz que lo define, <a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/HTMLCanvasElement\"><code>HTMLCanvasElement</code></a>.</li>\n <li>La otra propiedad que controla el tamaño del canvas,<a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/HTMLCanvasElement/height\"><code>HTMLCanvasElement.height</code></a>.</li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Syntax","id":"syntax"},{"text":"Ejemplos","id":"ejemplos"},{"text":"Especificaciones","id":"especificaciones"},{"text":"Compatibilidad de Navegadores","id":"compatibilidad_de_navegadores"},{"text":"Ver también","id":"see_also"}],"summary":"TLa propiedad  HTMLCanvasElement.width es un entero positivo que refleja el atributo width del elemento <canvas> interpretado en pixeles CSS. Cuando el atributo no esta especificado o se define con un valor invalido (ej. Número negativo), es usado el valor por defecto de 150.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"HTMLCanvasElement.width","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"HTMLCanvasElement.width","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"HTMLCanvasElement.width","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{